<li>Holding you and your family close in prayer.  May God's grace surround you.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, praying for comfort and strength during this difficult time.</li>
<li>I am so saddened to hear of your loss. May God bless you and your family.</li>
<li>May the love of God surround you and your family, bringing peace and comfort.</li>
<li>Thinking of you and your family during this time of sorrow. God's blessings be upon you.</li>
<li>Sending you and your family our deepest sympathy. May your faith guide you.</li>
<li>May God's love embrace you and your family, providing strength in your grief.</li>
<li>Please accept our sincere condolences. May God grant you eternal rest.</li>
<li>May the memories of your loved one bring you comfort and solace.</li>
<li>Praying for peace and healing for you and your family.</li>
